\mathbb{E}\left[\left|X_t\right|\right]\geq\left|\mathbb{E}\left[X_t\right]\right|= ae^{-bt}.
\mathbb{E}\left[X_t\right]^2+\mathrm{var}\left[X_t\right]=\mathbb{E}\left[X_t^2\right]=\mathbb{E}\left[\left|X_t\right|\right]^2+\mathrm{var}\left[\left|X_t\right|\right].
